    "title": "夏合宿（2年目）スタート！",
    "enTitle": "Summer Camp (Year 2) Begins!",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――夏合宿が始まる少し前の、ある日。",
            "enText": "A few days before the summer training \ncamp…",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 68,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": -2664695422417253317,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テレビの音声",
            "enName": "TV Voiceover",
            "jpText": "『――皐月賞とダービーで活躍した\n彼女の長期療養については、\nファンからも落胆の声があり――』",
            "enText": "\"Fans have been expressing their dejection \nafter her long term medical leave since \nparticipating in the Satsuki Sho and \nthe Derby —\"",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 106,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 248,
                    "pathId": 5023530416068767334
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 133,
                    "pathId": 6979724386543647618
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 133,
                    "pathId": -76902960799588096
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4435529970750846082,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "テレビの音声",
            "enName": "TV Voiceover",
            "jpText": "『――決してまぐれではない強さを\n示していましたからね。\n私も、菊花賞での走りを期待していて――』",
            "enText": "\"By no means however should you look down \non her strength. I'm also looking forward to \nher performance at the Kikuka Sho —\"",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 108,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 248,
                    "pathId": -6462815037267202581
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 119,
                    "pathId": 2058778072473502626
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 119,
                    "pathId": 8064007848284681026
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6432309809675889027,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "……縁が交わって、\n何か変わるかと思ったが――",
            "enText": "…Interacting with my destined connections, \nI thought something would change but ——",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 75,
            "voiceIdx": 35,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -1253951733803672248
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": -8534430159279621185
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 86,
                    "pathId": -6064698225003726312
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8284071228031843013,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "店主",
            "enName": "Shopkeeper",
            "jpText": "――はいよ、黄金味噌スペシャルね！\nチャーシュー、マシといたよ！",
            "enText": "—One up! Golden Miso Special! Got \nsome extra pork just for you!",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 67,
                    "pathId": 6517214733985876939
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": 7370821170761518590
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4773602709243722573,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "おおっ！？\n急にどうしたんだい、マスター。",
            "enText": "<i>Ohhhh!?</i> Master, what's this all of a sudden?",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "voiceIdx": 25,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 52,
                    "pathId": -6613430979318996053
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": 2278909351825605227
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 152739500410370933,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "店主",
            "enName": "Shopkeeper",
            "jpText": "『菊花賞』、出るんだろ？\n『皐月賞』からすっかりあんたのファンでさ！\n頑張れよ、応援してっから！",
            "enText": "You're running in that Kikuka Sho arent'cha? \nYour Satsuki Sho run made me an instant \nfan! Do ya best, coz I'm cheering you on!",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 107,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": -7445149899352430136
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 118,
                    "pathId": -5169504012991110975
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1331836535777875108,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "ハハッ、ありがとな！\nそんじゃ、遠慮なくいただくよ。\n期待しといてくれ。",
            "enText": "<i>Haha</i>, thanks a ton! I'll be digging in \nthen. Be sure to keep watching alright.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "voiceIdx": 12,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -5326386628322802414
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -1403119394447466240
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 373849524200264548,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "（変わるものと、変わらないものがある。\n……それだけのことか――）",
            "enText": "(Some things have changed, and other \nthings haven't… It's only that —)",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": 3603432653171398459
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": 8070400563883429327
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1269056102296042716,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そして、夏の日差しは強くなり――",
            "enText": "Then, the rays of the summer \nsun grew ever brighter —",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 23,
                    "pathId": 8042575439035872909
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 23,
                    "pathId": -7939446581864598196
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3226913514099403293,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "――『菊花賞』では、さらに強靭な\n心身のスタミナが求められます。",
            "enText": "—Gaining the stamina needed for the \nKikuka Sho requires you to fine tune \nyour mind and body.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "voiceIdx": 37,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": -8559720957408728801
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": 3963279446115743637
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": -2187698020321021689
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": -3477656674297411741
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5636893532821898266,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "それに夏の上がりウマ娘も台頭し、\n戦況も読みにくい……。あらゆる状況に\n対応できるよう、一層厳しくいきますわよ。",
            "enText": "Additionally, many girls shall rise in power \nthis summer, making the battlefield hard \nto predict… To fit any situation, we shall \nbe taking our training one step further.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 118,
            "voiceIdx": 90,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "合宿中も協力ありがとう、マックイーン",
                    "enText": "The support is truly appreciated, McQueen",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 129,
                    "pathId": 3850728478216194740
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 129,
                    "pathId": 3692758157734247027
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": -6128069459591603203
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 129,
                    "pathId": 5664750042896916469
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6819236777093551020,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "乗り掛かった船、ですわ。\n素晴らしい『皐月賞』と『日本ダービー』を\n見せてくれたお礼とでも思って下さいまし。",
            "enText": "Enough of that, I dare say. I would appreciate \nit if you instead treated this as my return \ngift for showing me such a wonderful \nSatsuki Sho and Japan Derby.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 115,
            "voiceIdx": 47,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": 4777429007425337955
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": -8620462918176921305
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 199,
                    "pathId": -8830293644771932009
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": 5680652864566797835
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": 6494617702206435902
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8292760996969192583,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "品のある栗毛のウマ娘",
            "enName": "$(scale 55)An Elegant Chestnut-Haired Horsegirl",
            "jpText": "夏合宿中の記録については、\n引き続き私に任せて下さい。\nステゴ様の力になれるよう、尽力します。",
            "enText": "Please leave it to myself to document \nthe results of this summer camp. I will \ndo my best to become someone Miss \nStego may rely upon.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 106,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 149,
                    "pathId": -7540755364687705451
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 117,
                    "pathId": 1413601831287190591
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 117,
                    "pathId": 6528760118456664574
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -3077903320070313933
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 117,
                    "pathId": 4530188796041615227
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 117,
                    "pathId": -2771309639728622016
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7998583571620767321,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "手厚いなぁ。\nおかげで今年は、随分熱い夏になりそうだ。",
            "enText": "You're a helpful one alright. Thanks to \nthat, this is gonna turn out becoming a \npretty heated-up summer.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 80,
            "voiceIdx": 31,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 129,
                    "pathId": -1156360533005001078
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 38,
                    "pathId": 6752824056646999086
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": 5028948791655657153
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 58,
                    "pathId": -4460160057441214791
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": -2149544688636686821
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5343358496227262361,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "……そうだ、マックイーン。\nブライトはどうしてる？",
            "enText": "…Oh that's right, McQueen. \nWhat's Bright doing?",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "voiceIdx": 52,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -786385127962063746
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 7696913083867157200
