                }
            ],
            "pathId": 9005944857411252515,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "秋以降の旅を、全力で楽しめるように。\nクラシック三冠を必ず走りきるために――",
            "enText": "Ever since autumn, we have been enjoying \nour journeys to the fullest. All so that we \ncan run for the Classic Triple Crown —",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": 2058073285921196821
                },
                {
