            "pathId": 1090929436401273924,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "そうだな。\n備えるとしよう。",
            "enText": "You're right. Let's aim for that.",
